that this user cares about

00:04:37.900 --> 00:04:38.325
your brand.

00:04:38.325 --> 00:04:41.580
There is an explicit signal
that they gave us

00:04:41.580 --> 00:04:43.100
by following you.

00:04:43.100 --> 00:04:46.030
So that goes way deeper than
just the brand query.

00:04:46.030 --> 00:04:48.860
Having that kind of an explicit
signal, explicit

00:04:48.860 --> 00:04:52.550
affirmation from the user that
they like you, that's the type

00:04:52.550 --> 00:04:55.480
