00:06:06.420 --> 00:06:07.830
For BMW, that made sense.

00:06:07.830 --> 00:06:09.020
They wanted that visual
experience.

00:06:09.020 --> 00:06:11.910
But for Verizon, they want to
maybe sell the product.

00:06:11.910 --> 00:06:16.305
So they included a link
to their product page.

