00:07:13.830 --> 00:07:17.460
Google's search results page
for people looking for you.

00:07:17.460 --> 00:07:20.270
And here, maybe you make direct
eye contact with the

00:07:20.270 --> 00:07:23.340
user who's searching for
you with your written

00:07:23.340 --> 00:07:26.480
message next to it.

00:07:26.480 --> 00:07:28.660
And not everything has to
have a time component.

