Google+ platform team released
Sign-In with Google

00:08:03.340 --> 00:08:06.050
functionality that I hope all
of you are considering or

00:08:06.050 --> 00:08:08.790
adopting to your website
and mobile app.

00:08:08.790 --> 00:08:12.790
So users come and login with
their Google ID to your

00:08:12.790 --> 00:08:15.780
service, be it on mobile
or desktop.

00:08:15.780 --> 00:08:19.160
Then with their consent, you
