recording is in this

00:24:31.330 --> 00:24:32.500
particular case, the
genre, and the

00:24:32.500 --> 00:24:33.870
language which it occurs.

00:24:33.870 --> 00:24:36.400
There may be a bunch of
additional data on the page.

00:24:36.400 --> 00:24:37.800
Now, that's fairly
straightforward.

00:24:37.800 --> 00:24:43.010
When Google's crawlers get to
this content, it allows us to

00:24:43.010 --> 00:24:46.080
